name: Doom-lloween
description:
Halloween last year was sad to hear that MF Doom passed away at 49, announced by his wife and also it surprised us who loved him

so I presented this Halloween with my character (Baldie-boy) to wear a Metal Mask of Daniel Dumile as known as MF Doom for reminiscing us while we can celebrate Halloween with his legacies till now and forever
MF DOOM WILL BE FOREVER
